               <p>ROBERT WIER SMITH. I <rs id="t18250113-78-viclabel409" type="occupation">keep a cheesemonger's-shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18250113-78-victim447 t18250113-78-viclabel409"></join>. On Saturday night last, a little before eleven o'clock, I was in my shop - there were some persons in the shop. I heard something fall on the opposite side; I looked over, and saw the head of a flat had fallen down, and a piece of pork was taken off it - I then looked, and saw the prisoner with it under her arm.</p>
               <p>
            
                  <persName id="t18250113-78-person448">
